WEBVTT

00:00:00.300 --> 00:00:03.737
Another Employee, Dylan, has been assigned a task he's

00:00:03.803 --> 00:00:05.205
worried he can't complete well.

00:00:05.271 --> 00:00:08.241
He knows that this task is related to an important

00:00:08.308 --> 00:00:11.878
competency for his position and has decided he needs to become

00:00:11.945 --> 00:00:13.613
more proficient.

00:00:13.680 --> 00:00:17.517
Article 21 an option for Dylan, too.

00:00:17.584 --> 00:00:21.154
Dylan can request remedial training for the task.

00:00:21.221 --> 00:00:25.625
The Department will determine if remedial training is appropriate for Dylan.

00:00:25.692 --> 00:00:28.261
If it is decided that training is appropriate,

00:00:28.328 --> 00:00:31.931
the Department will provide training in accordance with Article 23.


